                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div
                  class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-3 h-3 text-white"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  >
                    <path
                      fill-rule="evenodd"
                      d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"
                      clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">
                    Long Filter Life
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600">
                    Filter media last up to 3 years without replacement
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div
                  class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-3 h-3 text-white"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  >
                    <path
                      fill-rule="evenodd"
                      d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"
                      clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">
                    3-Year Warranty
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600">
                    Comprehensive warranty coverage
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Technical Specifications -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-8">
              Technical Specifications
            </h2>
            <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div
                  class="flex justify-between border-b border-neutral-200 pb-2"
                >
                  <span class="font-medium text-neutral-600">Material</span>
                  <span class="text-neutral-900">Hybrid Polymer PVDF</span>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex justify-between border-b border-neutral-200 pb-2"
                >
                  <span class="font-medium text-neutral-600">Dimension</span>
                  <span class="text-neutral-900"
                    >Height 1.5m × Width 0.4m × Length 0.6m</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex justify-between border-b border-neutral-200 pb-2"
                >
                  <span class="font-medium text-neutral-600"
                    >Diameter Bundle</span
                  >
                  <span class="text-neutral-900">Approximately 8 cm</span>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex justify-between border-b border-neutral-200 pb-2"
                >
                  <span class="font-medium text-neutral-600">Surface Area</span>
                  <span class="text-neutral-900">6 M2</span>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex justify-between border-b border-neutral-200 pb-2"
                >
                  <span class="font-medium text-neutral-600"
                    >Port Connection</span
                  >
                  <span class="text-neutral-900">3/4 inch pipe thread</span>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex justify-between border-b border-neutral-200 pb-2"
                >
                  <span class="font-medium text-neutral-600">Pore Size</span>
                  <span class="text-neutral-900">0.02 micron</span>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex justify-between border-b border-neutral-200 pb-2"
                >
                  <span class="font-medium text-neutral-600"
                    >Best Application</span
