        <p class="text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Contact us today for emergency preparedness planning and quotes for
          the TRAYA EU 6000-M system.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/#contact"
          class="btn bg-white text-red-800 hover:bg-neutral-50"
